8. Box Model & Layout Control 
.eventCard { 
border: 2px solid #007BFF; 
padding: 20px; 
margin: 15px auto; 
outline: none; 
} 
/* Highlight a selected form field */ 
input:focus { 
outline: 2px solid orange; 
} 
/* visibility vs display comparison */ 
.hidden-but-takes-space { 
visibility: hidden; /* element is invisible but still occupies layout space */ 
} 
.removed-from-layout { 
display: none; /* element is invisible and takes up no space at all */ 
} 
Open Chrome DevTools (right-click → Inspect → Computed/Box Model tab) on .eventCard to 
see the margin, border, padding, and content box drawn visually, and try dragging the values 
live to see how spacing changes. 

  
